{[#] This position illustrates the worst scenario for Black in the reversed
Carlsbad Structure. White managed to bring all his pieces into the attack. He
can now win by force:} 1. Rxh7+ $1 Kxh7 2. Nxg6 fxg6 3. Qxg6+ Kh8 4. Qh5+ Nh6 (
4... Kg7 5. Qh7+ Kf6 6. Qg6#) 5. Qxh6+ Kg8 6. Re3 {[%cal Ge3g3] with Rg3 to
follow. White is winning.} *

